<main>
    <section id="choose">
        <div class="wrapper">
            <img src="assets/nokia-n.png" alt="N">
            <div class="banner-overlay">
                <h2 class="display-1">Introduction</h2>
                <p class="overlay-text">First, <b>Log In</b> using your intra account. <br>
                    Then, <b>click your team</b> to start making reservations. <br>
                    Scroll down further for a walkthrough.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="reserve">
        <div class="wrapper">
            <img src="assets/nokia-o.png" alt="O">
            <div class="banner-overlay">
                <h2 class="display-1">Reserve a testline</h2>
                <p class="overlay-text">Go to the <b>Reservations</b> page and click 
                    <b>Use Now</b> or <b>Reserve Now</b> on the testlines that are available or in-use</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="queue">
        <div class="wrapper">
            <img src="assets/nokia-k.png" alt="K">
            <div class="banner-overlay">
                <h2 class="display-1">Who's in queue?</h2>
                <p class="overlay-text">Keep track of who's in line by going to the <b>Reservations</b> 
                    page, and select the testline you want to know who's in line for.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="release">
        <div class="wrapper">
            <img src="assets/nokia-i.png" alt="I">
            <div class="banner-overlay">
                <h2 class="display-1">Release a testline</h2>
                <p class="overlay-text">To <b>release a testline</b> you're currently using or 
                    <b>cancel a reservation</b>, click the reservations button in the navbar, 
                    select your testline, then click <b>release</b>.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="priority">
        <div class="wrapper">
            <img src="assets/nokia-a.png" alt="I">
            <div class="banner-overlay">
                <h2 class="display-1">Get Notified</h2>
                <p class="overlay-text">You can send someone an email notification by adding 
                    their email on the <b>Recipients</b> field before reserving on a testline to 
                    also give them notification when you've become the current user of the testline.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>